These are Puzzles for 4x3 Level 9

.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-9-1::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, sunflower, rose
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, fanta, almond-milk
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: parkour, basketball, skateboarding
House: wooden, cottage, townhouse
 1. the wooden house and the person drinking fanta have different parity positions##9
 2. the person drinking 7up is somewhere to the left of the cottage house##5
 3. the wooden house is not the person who growssunflower##6
 4. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
 5. the person drinking 7up and the person who growssunflower have different parity positions##9
 6. the person drinking almond-milk is the person who growsrose##1
 7. the wooden house is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is basketball##5
 8. the cottage house is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 9. the person drinking fanta and the person who growsrose have different parity positions##9
10. the person who's sport is parkour is the person drinking fanta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |    3     |
| Job           | balloon-flower | sunflower | rose    |
| Music-Genre   | 7up       | fanta   | almond-milk   |
| Nationality   | basketball    | parkour | skateboarding  |
| Transport     | townhouse   | cottage       | wooden |

