.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-9-2::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: bluemaster, pall-mall, vegafina
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: may, february, august
The people have 3 different jobs:  entrepreneur, videographer, designer
There are 3 different favourite colors: black, chestnut, pink
1. the person who's birthday is in february is somewhere to the right of the vegafina-smoker##5
2. the person who likes black is not to the right of the bluemaster-smoker##8
3. the entrepreneur is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in may##5
4. the entrepreneur and the pall-mall-smoker have the same parity positions##9
5. the person who's birthday is in may and the bluemaster-smoker have different parity positions##9
6. the person who's birthday is in august is in the middle##1
7. the person who likes chestnut is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in february##3
8. the designer is the person who's birthday is in august##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |     3     |
| Food          | vegafina  | bluemaster         | pall-mall |
| Hobby         | may | august | february   |
| Movie-Genre   | videographer     | designer       | entrepreneur     |
| Transport     | black       | chestnut          | pink    |

