3. the person who growslily is the colonial house##1
4. the gothic-revival house is on the left or right of the ranch-style house##3
5. the journalist is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to paris##5
6. the person who growsrose is on the right of the gothic-revival house##1
7. the pilot is not to the left of the person traveling to edinburgh##8
8. the person who growstulip and the person traveling to miami have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
