4. the modern house is in the middle##1
5. the person traveling to prague is on the far right##1
6. the futuristic house is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to hamburg##5
7. the futuristic house is in an odd position##4
8. the modern house is not to the right of the fan country##8

.:: Answer ::.
