The people prefer 3 different types of sport: volleyball, parkour, handball
1. the person traveling to colone is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to berlin##5
2. the person drinking soy-milk is somewhere to the right of the baccarat-smoker##5
3. the person who's sport is handball is between the havana-smoker and the person who's sport is volleyball##2
4. the person who's sport is parkour is not to the right of the person traveling to liverpool##8
5. the person traveling to liverpool and the person who's sport is parkour have the same parity positions##9
6. the person who's sport is parkour is somewhere to the right of the person drinking soy-milk##5
7. the baccarat-smoker is not to the left of the person traveling to colone##8
8. the person drinking hot-chocolate is not to the left of the person drinking soy-milk##8
9. the person drinking water is the person traveling to colone##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3    |
| Hobby         | colone  | berlin   | liverpool |
| Job           | baccarat   | vegafina | havana |
| Movie-Genre   | water   | soy-milk  | hot-chocolate     |
