 3. the person who's birthday is in january is not the person who growsaconite##6
 4. the person who growsrose and the owner of the cat have different parity positions##9
 5. the person who growsaconite is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the person playing scrabble is not the owner of the horse##6
 7. the person playing canasta and the person who's birthday is in march have different parity positions##9
 8. the person playing canasta is somewhere to the left of the owner of the horse##5
 9. the person playing poker is somewhere to the right of the owner of the turtle##5
10. the person who's birthday is in march and the person playing scrabble have the same parity positions##9
11. the person who growszinnia is on the far left##1
12. the owner of the turtle is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |      2       |      3      |
